text: Thomas Lundgren (born 25 October 1956) is a Swedish ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill event at the 1976 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Sweden Category:Ski jumpers at the 1976 Winter Olympics Category:People from Örnsköldsvik Municipality
